OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779005164
OL,3,C'Unprecedented' police operation in
OL,4,Ccapital as tens of thousands to protest
OL,6,FAround 4,000 officers are expected to
OL,7,Fbe on duty on Saturday, with 660 being
OL,8,Fdrafted in from forces outside the Met.
OL,10,FSir Keir asked about protester numbers
OL,11,Fduring his Lambeth visit, with police
OL,12,Festimating around 50,000 people set to
OL,13,Fattend the Unite the Kingdom rally,
OL,14,Fand 30,000 at Nakba Day.
OL,16,FMetropolitan Police Deputy Assistant
OL,17,FCommissioner James Harman said the
OL,18,Fpolicing operation will cost the force
OL,19,F#4.5 million, with #1.7 million being
OL,20,Fused on bringing in officers from
OL,21,Fother forces to boost numbers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779005164
OL,3,C'Unprecedented' police operation in
OL,4,Ccapital as tens of thousands to protest
OL,6,FHe said the operation was taking place
OL,7,Fagainst a backdrop of "continued
OL,8,Fglobal instability and tension",
OL,9,Fincreased antisemitism, concerns
OL,10,Fwithin Jewish and Muslim communities,
OL,11,Fand a severe terrorism threat level.
OL,13,FDowning Street said law-abiding
OL,14,Fprotesters would continue to be
OL,15,Fprotected, but warned that anyone
OL,16,Fattempting to "break the law and
OL,17,Fcreate chaos" should expect to "feel
OL,18,Fthe full force of the law".
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@_O]xD@OOUyD@MO]yD@`OUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779005164
OL,3,C'Unprecedented' police operation in
OL,4,Ccapital as tens of thousands to protest
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Metropolitan Police
OL,7,FFederation said many officers have had
OL,8,Fleave cancelled and rest days
OL,9,Fwithdrawn to meet policing
OL,10,Frequirements, adding: "There are not
OL,11,Fenough of us."
OL,13,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said:
OL,14,F"The right to protest is a cornerstone
OL,15,Fof our democracy. But anyone spreading
OL,16,Fhate or committing acts of violence
OL,17,Fwill face the full force of the law."
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@NO]vD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
